  linesWarn:
  - Hey... uh, got a sec?
  - Listen, I just need to check something real quick.
  - You picked a bad day, man. I'm already running late.
  linesDemandBribe:
  - Look, if you just... you know... we can both go home.
  - I really do not want to do paperwork tonight. Just saying.
  - Make it easy and we both walk away happy.
  linesAcceptBribe:
  - Alright, we're good. Have a nice evening.
  - I didn't see anything.
  - ...Yeah. That works.
  linesRejectBribe:
  - Come on, man. Don't make me work.
  - Really? Fine. Fine, we'll do it the hard way.
  linesArrest:
  - You're making this way harder than it needs to be.
  - I hate days like this. I really do.
  linesAttack:
  - Seriously? It's almost end of shift.
  - I do NOT want to write this report.
